==English==
=== Etymology ===
From ''[[Nippon]]'', native name for Japan

===Verb===
{{en-verb|nipponiz|es}}

# {{transitive}} To make [[Japanese]], as to customs, culture, or style
# {{transitive}} To [[port]] or [[migrate]] to [[Japan]]
# {{transitive}} To translate into Japanese
# {{transitive}} To make a [[kana]] spelling of (a word or name)

